---
title: Pistachio Cake & Berry Compote with White Chocolate Ganache | Serves 6
description: We've kicked it up a notch with this cake that's three parts light, buttery and nutty. Iced with a white chocolate ganache, then sprinkled with pistachios for a little crunch and served with a berry compote, it's the ultimate afternoon delight!
